{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-blog-post-tsx","path":"/2019/06/01/power-shell-core","result":{"data":{"site":{"siteMetadata":{"title":"<bbon />","siteUrl":"https://bbon.me"}},"markdownRemark":{"id":"82e6ecfe-e1f0-5dae-bcc8-069265064687","excerpt":"작업을 시작하기 위해 파워쉘을 열었는데, 평소와는 다른 메시지가 출력됩니다. 궁금해서 https://aka.ms/pscore6 링크로 이동하니 다양한 버전의 PowerShell 설치 Installing various versions of PowerShell…","html":"<p>작업을 시작하기 위해 파워쉘을 열었는데, 평소와는 다른 메시지가 출력됩니다.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"powershell\"><pre class=\"language-powershell\"><code class=\"language-powershell\">Windows PowerShell\nCopyright <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>C<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> Microsoft Corporation<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span> All rights reserved<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>\n\n<span class=\"token keyword\">Try</span> the new cross-platform PowerShell https:<span class=\"token operator\">/</span><span class=\"token operator\">/</span>aka<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>ms/pscore6</code></pre></div>\n<p>궁금해서 <a href=\"https://aka.ms/pscore6\">https://aka.ms/pscore6</a> 링크로 이동하니 <a href=\"https://docs.microsoft.com/ko-kr/powershell/scripting/install/installing-powershell?view=powershell-6#powershell-core\">다양한 버전의 PowerShell 설치 <small>Installing various versions of PowerShell</small></a> 페이지가 열립니다.</p>\n<p>페이지 아래쪽에 PowerShell Core 라는 제목이 보이고 아래와 같은 링크들이 있습니다.</p>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://docs.microsoft.com/ko-kr/powershell/scripting/install/installing-powershell-core-on-windows?view=powershell-6\">Installing PowerShell Core on Windows</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://docs.microsoft.com/ko-kr/powershell/scripting/install/installing-powershell-core-on-linux?view=powershell-6\">Installing PowerShell Core on Linux</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://docs.microsoft.com/ko-kr/powershell/scripting/install/installing-powershell-core-on-macos?view=powershell-6\">Installing PowerShell Core on macOS</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://docs.microsoft.com/ko-kr/powershell/scripting/install/powershell-core-on-arm?view=powershell-6\">Installing PowerShell Core on ARM</a></li>\n</ul>\n<p>파워쉘은 Windows 에서만 사용할 수 있었는데, 이제 다른 OS에서도 파워쉘을 사용할 수 있습니다.</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://github.com/powershell/powershell\">GitHub</a> 에서 코드를 공개하고 있습니다.</p>\n<h2>설치</h2>\n<h3>Windows 10</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://github.com/PowerShell/PowerShell/releases/latest\">GitHub 출시 <small>Release</small> 페이지</a> 에서 설치 파일을 다운로드할 수 있습니다.</p>\n<h3>Linux</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://github.com/PowerShell/PowerShell/releases/latest\">GitHub 출시 <small>Release</small> 페이지</a> 에서 설치 파일을 다운로드할 수 있고, 편리하게 패키지 관리자로 설치할 수 있습니다.</p>\n<p>Ubuntu, Debian 에서</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"bash\"><pre class=\"language-bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\">$ <span class=\"token function\">sudo</span> <span class=\"token function\">apt-get</span> <span class=\"token function\">install</span> powershell</code></pre></div>\n<p>CentOS, RedHat 에서</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"bash\"><pre class=\"language-bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\">$ <span class=\"token function\">sudo</span> yum <span class=\"token function\">install</span> powershell</code></pre></div>\n<p>Fedora 에서</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"bash\"><pre class=\"language-bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\">$ <span class=\"token function\">sudo</span> dnf <span class=\"token function\">install</span> powershell</code></pre></div>\n<h3>macOS</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://github.com/PowerShell/PowerShell/releases/latest\">GitHub 출시 Release 페이지</a> 에서 설치 파일을 다운로드할 수 있고, 편리하게 패키지 관리자로 설치할 수 있습니다.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"bash\"><pre class=\"language-bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\">$ brew cask <span class=\"token function\">install</span> powershell</code></pre></div>\n<h3>ARM</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://docs.microsoft.com/ko-kr/powershell/scripting/install/installing-powershell-core-on-windows?view=powershell-6#deploying-on-windows-iot\">Windows IoT</a> 와 <a href=\"https://docs.microsoft.com/ko-kr/powershell/scripting/install/installing-powershell-core-on-linux?view=powershell-6#raspbian\">Raspbian</a> 에서 설치하는 방법이 설명되어 있습니다.</p>\n<h2>실행</h2>\n<p>설치하면서 환경변수 PATH 에 설치되는 위치가 추가되므로 자주 사용하는 터미널 응용프로그램을 열고 <code class=\"language-text\">PWSH</code> 명령으로 PowerShell Core 를 실행할 수 있습니다.</p>\n<p>시작메뉴에서 검색하면 PowerShell 6 으로 찾을 수 있습니다.</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 340px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/a3eedf11d0dc529b15fe2d3b73ac579b/f46e7/2019-06-01-powershell-core-004.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 200%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <picture>\n          <source\n              srcset=\"/static/a3eedf11d0dc529b15fe2d3b73ac579b/18dfc/2019-06-01-powershell-core-004.webp 158w,\n/static/a3eedf11d0dc529b15fe2d3b73ac579b/30002/2019-06-01-powershell-core-004.webp 315w,\n/static/a3eedf11d0dc529b15fe2d3b73ac579b/719ab/2019-06-01-powershell-core-004.webp 340w\"\n              sizes=\"(max-width: 340px) 100vw, 340px\"\n              type=\"image/webp\"\n            />\n          <source\n            srcset=\"/static/a3eedf11d0dc529b15fe2d3b73ac579b/4d6f2/2019-06-01-powershell-core-004.png 158w,\n/static/a3eedf11d0dc529b15fe2d3b73ac579b/3c1ae/2019-06-01-powershell-core-004.png 315w,\n/static/a3eedf11d0dc529b15fe2d3b73ac579b/f46e7/2019-06-01-powershell-core-004.png 340w\"\n            sizes=\"(max-width: 340px) 100vw, 340px\"\n            type=\"image/png\"\n          />\n          <img\n            class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n            src=\"/static/a3eedf11d0dc529b15fe2d3b73ac579b/f46e7/2019-06-01-powershell-core-004.png\"\n            alt=\"2019 06 01 powershell core 004\"\n            title=\"2019 06 01 powershell core 004\"\n            loading=\"lazy\"\n            decoding=\"async\"\n            style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n          />\n        </picture>\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<h2>사용</h2>\n<p>Windows 10 에서 설치를 진행합니다.</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://github.com/PowerShell/PowerShell/releases/latest\">GitHub 출시 페이지</a> 에서 PowerShell-6.2.1-win-x64.msi 파일을 다운로드하고 실행하면 간단하게 설치됩니다.</p>\n<p>설치 마법사에서 아래와 같이 환경변수에 설치 경로 추가 등의 항목을 선택하면 간단하게 편리한 환경을 구성할 수 있습니다.</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 495px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/07b3f3996701583ea7ad6099eab4f799/68bae/2019-06-01-powershell-core-001.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 78.48101265822784%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <picture>\n          <source\n              srcset=\"/static/07b3f3996701583ea7ad6099eab4f799/18dfc/2019-06-01-powershell-core-001.webp 158w,\n/static/07b3f3996701583ea7ad6099eab4f799/30002/2019-06-01-powershell-core-001.webp 315w,\n/static/07b3f3996701583ea7ad6099eab4f799/49d8f/2019-06-01-powershell-core-001.webp 495w\"\n              sizes=\"(max-width: 495px) 100vw, 495px\"\n              type=\"image/webp\"\n            />\n          <source\n            srcset=\"/static/07b3f3996701583ea7ad6099eab4f799/4d6f2/2019-06-01-powershell-core-001.png 158w,\n/static/07b3f3996701583ea7ad6099eab4f799/3c1ae/2019-06-01-powershell-core-001.png 315w,\n/static/07b3f3996701583ea7ad6099eab4f799/68bae/2019-06-01-powershell-core-001.png 495w\"\n            sizes=\"(max-width: 495px) 100vw, 495px\"\n            type=\"image/png\"\n          />\n          <img\n            class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n            src=\"/static/07b3f3996701583ea7ad6099eab4f799/68bae/2019-06-01-powershell-core-001.png\"\n            alt=\"2019 06 01 powershell core 001\"\n            title=\"2019 06 01 powershell core 001\"\n            loading=\"lazy\"\n            decoding=\"async\"\n            style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n          />\n        </picture>\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>윈도우 파워쉘과 유사한 아이콘이 사용됩니다.</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 100px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/f0728ebe46c6121ecb7ae6fb25cc4204/effb6/2019-06-01-powershell-core-002.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 61%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <picture>\n          <source\n              srcset=\"/static/f0728ebe46c6121ecb7ae6fb25cc4204/e976a/2019-06-01-powershell-core-002.webp 100w\"\n              sizes=\"(max-width: 100px) 100vw, 100px\"\n              type=\"image/webp\"\n            />\n          <source\n            srcset=\"/static/f0728ebe46c6121ecb7ae6fb25cc4204/effb6/2019-06-01-powershell-core-002.png 100w\"\n            sizes=\"(max-width: 100px) 100vw, 100px\"\n            type=\"image/png\"\n          />\n          <img\n            class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n            src=\"/static/f0728ebe46c6121ecb7ae6fb25cc4204/effb6/2019-06-01-powershell-core-002.png\"\n            alt=\"2019 06 01 powershell core 002\"\n            title=\"2019 06 01 powershell core 002\"\n            loading=\"lazy\"\n            decoding=\"async\"\n            style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n          />\n        </picture>\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>터미널을 열고 PWSH 명령으로 PowerShell Core 를 실행하고, PowerShell 명령으로 Windows PowerShell을 실행할 수 있습니다.</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 460px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/5b2b3acb750dd26a503db6687dbb8aaf/610aa/2019-06-01-powershell-core-003.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 75.31645569620254%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <picture>\n          <source\n              srcset=\"/static/5b2b3acb750dd26a503db6687dbb8aaf/18dfc/2019-06-01-powershell-core-003.webp 158w,\n/static/5b2b3acb750dd26a503db6687dbb8aaf/30002/2019-06-01-powershell-core-003.webp 315w,\n/static/5b2b3acb750dd26a503db6687dbb8aaf/41b05/2019-06-01-powershell-core-003.webp 460w\"\n              sizes=\"(max-width: 460px) 100vw, 460px\"\n              type=\"image/webp\"\n            />\n          <source\n            srcset=\"/static/5b2b3acb750dd26a503db6687dbb8aaf/4d6f2/2019-06-01-powershell-core-003.png 158w,\n/static/5b2b3acb750dd26a503db6687dbb8aaf/3c1ae/2019-06-01-powershell-core-003.png 315w,\n/static/5b2b3acb750dd26a503db6687dbb8aaf/610aa/2019-06-01-powershell-core-003.png 460w\"\n            sizes=\"(max-width: 460px) 100vw, 460px\"\n            type=\"image/png\"\n          />\n          <img\n            class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n            src=\"/static/5b2b3acb750dd26a503db6687dbb8aaf/610aa/2019-06-01-powershell-core-003.png\"\n            alt=\"2019 06 01 powershell core 003\"\n            title=\"2019 06 01 powershell core 003\"\n            loading=\"lazy\"\n            decoding=\"async\"\n            style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n          />\n        </picture>\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<h2>Visual Studio Code Terminal</h2>\n<p>Visual Studio Code 에서 기본 터미널로 설정하기 위해서 설정창을 열고 <kbd>Ctrl</kbd> + <kbd>,</kbd> 검색창에 terminal 을 입력한 후 <code class=\"language-text\">Terminal > Integrated > Env:Windows</code> 항목을 찾습니다.</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 630px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/701db1b079a075894a7fc8d0877fbcc7/90cda/2019-06-01-powershell-core-005.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 87.9746835443038%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <picture>\n          <source\n              srcset=\"/static/701db1b079a075894a7fc8d0877fbcc7/18dfc/2019-06-01-powershell-core-005.webp 158w,\n/static/701db1b079a075894a7fc8d0877fbcc7/30002/2019-06-01-powershell-core-005.webp 315w,\n/static/701db1b079a075894a7fc8d0877fbcc7/e59cf/2019-06-01-powershell-core-005.webp 630w,\n/static/701db1b079a075894a7fc8d0877fbcc7/bfe67/2019-06-01-powershell-core-005.webp 637w\"\n              sizes=\"(max-width: 630px) 100vw, 630px\"\n              type=\"image/webp\"\n            />\n          <source\n            srcset=\"/static/701db1b079a075894a7fc8d0877fbcc7/4d6f2/2019-06-01-powershell-core-005.png 158w,\n/static/701db1b079a075894a7fc8d0877fbcc7/3c1ae/2019-06-01-powershell-core-005.png 315w,\n/static/701db1b079a075894a7fc8d0877fbcc7/984b6/2019-06-01-powershell-core-005.png 630w,\n/static/701db1b079a075894a7fc8d0877fbcc7/90cda/2019-06-01-powershell-core-005.png 637w\"\n            sizes=\"(max-width: 630px) 100vw, 630px\"\n            type=\"image/png\"\n          />\n          <img\n            class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n            src=\"/static/701db1b079a075894a7fc8d0877fbcc7/984b6/2019-06-01-powershell-core-005.png\"\n            alt=\"2019 06 01 powershell core 005\"\n            title=\"2019 06 01 powershell core 005\"\n            loading=\"lazy\"\n            decoding=\"async\"\n            style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n          />\n        </picture>\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>아래쪽의 Edit in settings.json 링크를 클릭해서 설정 파일을 열고, <code class=\"language-text\">terminal.integrated.shell.windows</code> 의 값을 PowerShell Core 실행파일의 전체 경로로 변경합니다.</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 608px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/0754b5c62ecfb671faddce5e04147dd6/5db90/2019-06-01-powershell-core-006.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 6.962025316455696%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,iVBORw0KGgoAAAANSUhEUgAAABQAAAABCAYAAADeko4lAAAACXBIWXMAAA7DAAAOwwHHb6hkAAAATUlEQVQI1xXJSw6AIAxAQe+hlYURKcX4JUKM3v9WzzjbaSzN1PtlPzJXuSn1IefCuS4c287gR8R7xJTOAqIBSZE2KRIVZ0b3X5zoneMDzHIeBge0odgAAAAASUVORK5CYII='); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <picture>\n          <source\n              srcset=\"/static/0754b5c62ecfb671faddce5e04147dd6/18dfc/2019-06-01-powershell-core-006.webp 158w,\n/static/0754b5c62ecfb671faddce5e04147dd6/30002/2019-06-01-powershell-core-006.webp 315w,\n/static/0754b5c62ecfb671faddce5e04147dd6/dfa82/2019-06-01-powershell-core-006.webp 608w\"\n              sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\"\n              type=\"image/webp\"\n            />\n          <source\n            srcset=\"/static/0754b5c62ecfb671faddce5e04147dd6/4d6f2/2019-06-01-powershell-core-006.png 158w,\n/static/0754b5c62ecfb671faddce5e04147dd6/3c1ae/2019-06-01-powershell-core-006.png 315w,\n/static/0754b5c62ecfb671faddce5e04147dd6/5db90/2019-06-01-powershell-core-006.png 608w\"\n            sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\"\n            type=\"image/png\"\n          />\n          <img\n            class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n            src=\"/static/0754b5c62ecfb671faddce5e04147dd6/5db90/2019-06-01-powershell-core-006.png\"\n            alt=\"2019 06 01 powershell core 006\"\n            title=\"2019 06 01 powershell core 006\"\n            loading=\"lazy\"\n            decoding=\"async\"\n            style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n          />\n        </picture>\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"json\"><pre class=\"language-json\"><code class=\"language-json\"><span class=\"token property\">\"terminal.integrated.shell.windows\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"C:\\\\Program Files\\\\PowerShell\\\\6\\\\pwsh.exe\"</span></code></pre></div>\n<p>이제 Visual Studio Code 에서 터미널을 열면 <kbd>Ctrl</kbd> + <kbd>`</kbd> 터미널에서 PowerShell Core 가 사용됩니다.</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 630px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/e5ea6f16b7b987dfbe818c47c91d2661/41929/2019-06-01-powershell-core-007.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\